This dataset has been published in the following paper:

Kobayashi, K., Lee, S., Filipowicz, A. L. S., McGaughey, K. D., Kable, J. W. & Nassar, M. R. Dynamic representation of the subjective value of information. bioRxiv, https://doi.org/10.1101/2021.02.12.431038.
 
15 participants completed a modified "beads task" paradigm, in which they decided whether to acquire costly information, across four scanning runs. In addition to raw data under sub-\*/, preprocessed data are available under derivatives/fsl/sub-\*/. 

Code for behavioral modeling are available at gitlab.com/kenji.k/beadsVOI/. Unthresholded group-level statistics maps are available at https://neurovault.org/collections/MORTKKAM/.
